<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id4d408a62-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d" identifier="/us/usc/t34/s21905"><num value="21905">§ 21905.</num><heading> Voluntary participation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The minimum standards established under <ref href="/us/usc/t34/s21904/a">section 21904(a) of this title</ref>, and any other guidelines and programs established under <ref href="/us/usc/t34/s21903">section 21903 of this title</ref>, shall be adoptable on a voluntary basis only.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id4d408a63-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d">(<ref href="/us/pl/106/468/tII/s205">Pub. L. 106–468, title II, § 205</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/115/401/s2/5">Pub. L. 115–401, § 2(5)</ref>, <date date="2018-12-31">Dec. 31, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/5341">132 Stat. 5341</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
